OL,3,CSir Ed Davey calls carers overpayments
OL,4,Ca 'scandal of huge proportions'
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrat leader Sir Ed
OL,7,FDavey has welcomed a review into what
OL,8,Fhe has called "a scandal of huge
OL,9,Fproportions" where thousands of unpaid
OL,10,Fcarers are being asked to pay back
OL,11,Flarge sums of money to the Department
OL,12,Fof Work & Pensions (DWP).
OL,14,FCharities have warned of the toll the
OL,15,FCarer's Allowance overpayments has had
OL,16,Fon "vulnerable people", that has
OL,17,Fcaused carers to rack up debt,
OL,18,Fsometimes as high as #20,000, after
OL,19,Funwittingly falling foul of benefit
OL,20,Frules.
