OL,3,CSir Ed Davey calls carers overpayments
OL,4,Ca 'scandal of huge proportions'
OL,6,FMany were threatened with criminal
OL,7,Fprosecution over breaches of earning
OL,8,Flimits, with some only going over the
OL,9,Fworking hours by a few minutes. It's
OL,10,Fthought 134,500 people are impacted,
OL,11,Fwith about #251m in overpayments being
OL,12,Fclaimed by the DWP.
OL,14,FIt comes as Liz Kendall, the secretary
OL,15,Fof state for work and pensions,
OL,16,Flaunched an independent review of
OL,17,Foverpayments to assess how they were
OL,18,Faccrued.
