OL,6,FWhen asked whether a blanket policy is
OL,7,Fthe right way forward and if all debts
OL,8,Fshould be cancelled, the Lib Dem
OL,9,Fleader said if "really egregious
OL,10,Fexamples of fraud" have taken place,
OL,11,Fthey should be "punished."
OL,13,FHe has called for the debts of people
OL,14,F"who are being chased and persecuted,
OL,15,Ffrankly, by the DWP" to be written off.
