OL,6,FSir Ed said "I challenged the
OL,7,FConservatives in the Commons...on a
OL,8,Fmotion to draw to attention to this
OL,9,Fproblem, and they clearly, failed to
OL,10,Fdo a proper job when they were in
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"It's a scandal of huge proportions,
OL,14,Fwe're looking at tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fpeople being pursued by the Department
OL,16,Ffor Work and Pensions, for the
OL,17,Fincompetence of the Department of Work
OL,18,Fand Pensions. That's just wrong.
