OL,4,Ca 'scandal of huge proportions'
OL,6,F"And I really hope Labour ministers
OL,7,Fget a grip of this. Given the
OL,8,FConservatives failed for the whole of
OL,9,Fthe last Parliament."
OL,11,FA recent study of 12,500 unpaid carers
OL,12,Fby Carers UK called 'State of Caring
OL,13,FSurvey 2024' found...
OL,15,FIn a Debate in parliament last week,
OL,16,Fwhen challenged by Sir Ed on their
OL,17,Ftime in power for handling carer's
OL,18,Fallowance, Mel Stride MP defended the
OL,19,FConservatives handling of the matter.
