OL,3,CSir Ed Davey calls carers overpayments
OL,4,Ca 'scandal of huge proportions'
OL,6,F"When we were in government, we
OL,7,Fbrought forward a number of measures
OL,8,Fto make sure we supported those
OL,9,Fcarers. The level of carer's allowance
OL,10,Fitself has increased by #1500 from
OL,11,F2010.
OL,13,F"There's an element of trust in how
OL,14,Fthat benefit works...therefore there
OL,15,Fis an earnings limit."
